   Write a program with the following requirements:

   a. Create a turtle and give it your name
   b. Ask the user (input) what color they want the background to be.
   c. Change the color of your turtle for each letter
   d. Change the pen size for your turtle
   e. Make your turtle spell out your name or initials with different colors
   f. Make one extra embellishment on your drawing (this could be a flower, a sun, a smiley face etcâ€¦)
